<body class="bg-bg-deep font-sans text-text-muted antialiased">

    <!-- BARRA TOPO: FOMENTO DE OPÇÃO REAL -->
    <div class="bg-accent text-bg-deep text-center p-3 font-bold sticky top-0 z-50 text-sm md:text-base shadow-md uppercase tracking-wider">
        <span>⚠️ AVISO: Bônus de Suporte para Emissão de Visto Grátis Hoje!</span>
    </div>

    <!-- HERO SECTION: O ALVO PRINCIPAL -->
    <header class="bg-bg-deep py-12 md:py-20 border-b border-border-dark overflow-hidden">
        <div class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-center">
                <div class="text-center md:text-left order-2 md:order-1">
                    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold leading-tight text-text-main">
                        A Enciclopédia Real do Trecho: O Guia Definitivo do Garimpeiro no Suriname.
                    </h1>
                    <p class="mt-6 text-base md:text-lg text-text-muted">Não entre na mata às盲gas. Descubra a rota exata da logística, sobrevivência real em currutelas, funcionamento técnico de motores e a blindagem contra os golpes do norte.</p>
                    
                    <ul class="mt-8 space-y-4 text-left inline-block md:block">
                        <li class="flex items-start">
                            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
                            <span class="text-text-main text-sm md:text-base">Para quem quer pisar no Suriname 100% legalizado, livre de prisões e extorsões de fronteira.</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start">
                            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
                            <span class="text-text-main text-sm md:text-base">Para quem precisa dominar o funcionamento de máquinas, PC e o sistema de Meia-Praça.</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start">
                            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
                            <span class="text-text-main text-sm md:text-base">Para quem busca o Bambúrrio financeiro, mas exige blindar a própria vida contra a Malária e traições.</span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    
                    <div class="mt-10">
                        <a href="#offer" class="inline-block w-full md:w-auto bg-accent text-bg-deep font-bold text-lg md:text-xl py-4 px-8 rounded-lg shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(212,175,55,0.3)] hover:bg-accent-hover hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 uppercase tracking-tight">
                            Quero Acessar o Guia do Trecho
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="order-1 md:order-2 flex justify-center w-full px-4 sm:px-8 md:px-0">
                    <!-- Henrique deve subir a imagem 3D do e-book dele aqui -->
                    <img src="https://i.postimg.cc/C5KMyFZv/capa-pare-de-procrastinar-3-em-1.png" alt="Capa da Enciclopédia Real do Trecho" class="w-full max-w-sm md:max-w-full h-auto object-contain rounded-lg drop-shadow-[0_0_25px_rgba(212,175,55,0.15)]">
                </div>
