                    <h3 class="font-bold text-text-main text-lg flex items-center">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 mr-3 text-accent" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M5 3a2 2 0 00-2 2v2a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5zM5 11a2 2 0 00-2 2v2a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2v-2a2 2 0 00-2-2H5zM11 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v2a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2V5zM11 13a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v2a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2v-2z"></path></svg>
                        Dicionário Exclusivo do Trecho
                    </h3>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-bg-card p-6 rounded-xl border border-border-dark hover:border-accent/50 transition-colors shadow-lg">
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-text-main text-lg flex items-center">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 mr-3 text-accent" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M11.3 1.046A1 1 0 0112 2v5h4a1 1 0 01.82 1.573l-7 10A1 1 0 018 18v-5H4a1 1 0 01-.82-1.573l7-10a1 1 0 011.12-.38z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
                        Farmácia Anti-Malária Rígida
                    </h3>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-bg-card p-6 rounded-xl border border-border-dark hover:border-accent/50 transition-colors shadow-lg">
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-text-main text-lg flex items-center">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 mr-3 text-accent" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M10 12a2 2 0 100-4 2 2 0 000 4z"></path><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M.458 10C1.732 5.943 5.522 3 10 3s8.268 2.943 9.542 7c-1.274 4.057-5.022 7-9.542 7S1.732 14.057.458 10zM14 10a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
                        Segurança Antitradição em Grotas
                    </h3>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-bg-card p-6 rounded-xl border border-border-dark hover:border-accent/50 transition-colors shadow-lg">
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-text-main text-lg flex items-center">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 mr-3 text-accent" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M3 3a1 1 0 000 2v8a1 1 0 001 1h1.586l.707.707a1 1 0 001.414 0L7.414 14H9a1 1 0 001-1V5a1 1 0 00-1-1H4a1 1 0 00-1-1zm13 0a1 1 0 00-1 1v4a1 1 0 001 1h1.586l.707.707a1 1 0 001.414 0L19.414 10H21a1 1 0 001-1V5a1 1 0 00-1-1h-5z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
                        Contratação nas Janelas de Verão
                    </h3>
                </div>
             </div>
